<P>__{(still smiling)}
<D>__{it doesn't make any difference about me, but one of these days you're going to find out that all this charm of yours won't be enough }
<C>__{kane}
<P>__{(has stopped dancing)}
<D>__{you're wrong. it does make a difference to you rector's, brad?}
<P>__{(starts to dance again)}
<D>__{come to think of it, i don't blame you for not wanting to be a war correspondent. you won't miss anything. it isn't much of a war. besides, they tell me there isn't a decent restaurant on the whole island.}
